  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for research on barriers to women&#x2019;s economic empowerment and economic growth in low-income countries&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This grant would supplement the Growth and Economic Opportunities for Women (GrOW) research initiative, a five-year partnership with the U.K.&#x2019;s Department for International Development and Canada&#x2019;s International Development Research Centre. The initiative aims to support research to guide policies and programs that improve women&#x2019;s economic empowerment in low-income countries. The supplemental funding will allow GrOW to include four additional research projects on how patterns of economic growth impact gender equality, and a systematic review of how women&#x2019;s economic empowerment impacts growth.  &quot;</narrative>
  </description>
